title: Snatched! Curse of the Pink Panties II [2010 - USA] comedy
description:
Snatched! (2010 - USA)                           aka Curse of the Pink Panties II

Comedy / Crime / Mystery

Cranium Candy Entertainment Production Company
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1210047/


The spirits are back in this bizarre sequel to Curse of the Pink Panties. A vicious shootout leaves all but one of a group of gangsters dead. The Evil ones are using black magic to stop the dead gangsters' spirits from descending to their afterlife. Now, the gangsta ghosts conjure up a plan to evade the Evil ones by hiding in the panties of beautiful girls. Lovely Faith discovers a package with a pair of pink panties in it and slides into them. As she begins to put on a sexy show for her boyfriend, Judd, the spirits attack Judd and then kidnap her. Judd joins with Guido, the only gangster to survive the shootout. An intense search begins to rescue the girls, find the Evil ones, and send the gangsta ghosts packing! But can Judd, Guido and their team get things under control before time runs out?
